org.knime.core.node.workflow

Class FlowTryCatchContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.workflow.FlowObject
      • org.knime.core.node.workflow.FlowScopeContext
        • org.knime.core.node.workflow.FlowTryCatchContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public final class FlowTryCatchContext
extends FlowScopeContext
    Pushed on top of the stack inside a try-catch construct. Stores reasons for failures that are caught by the WorkflowManager to be reported by the catch node.
    Since:
    2.8
    Author:
    M. Berthold, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
